---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Best Shopify Email Apps for Gift Cards in 2026';
const description = 'Compare Shopify email apps for gift-card marketing by gifting intent, delivery, redemption, segmentation, pricing context, sources, and tradeoffs.';
const apps = [['Klaviyo','Gift-card intent and recipient-aware journeys','Detailed profiles, events, and conditional flows','Gift and recipient data need careful boundaries','https://www.klaviyo.com/features/segmentation'],['Omnisend','Retail gift-card campaigns across email and SMS','Accessible promotional automation','Gift timing and frequency require discipline','https://www.omnisend.com/features/marketing-automation/'],['Sequenzy','Lean stores with simple gift-card sequences','Focused gifting and redemption workflows','Validate gift-card event support','https://sequenzy.io/'],['Brevo','Gift-card marketing beside transactional delivery','Broad messaging and contact options','More manual redemption-state modeling','https://www.brevo.com/features/marketing-automation/'],['Shopify Email','Simple native gift-card announcements','Fast product and campaign setup','Limited recipient-aware branching','https://www.shopify.com/email-marketing']];
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}><main class="container page-stack"><p class="eyebrow">Shopify email apps</p><h1>{title}</h1><p class="lede">Gift-card email has two audiences: the purchaser and the recipient. The store should deliver the gift accurately, explain redemption without clutter, and avoid treating an unredeemed balance as a generic abandoned cart.</p><p>We prioritize gifting intent, delivery state, redemption events, and post-purchase suppression. Confirm current pricing and gift-card integration behavior from official sources before launch.</p><h2>Shortlist for gift-card programs</h2><table><thead><tr><th>App</th><th>Best fit</th><th>First gift-card path</th><th>Tradeoff</th></tr></thead><tbody>{apps.map(a=><tr><td>{a[0]}</td><td>{a[1]}</td><td>{a[0]==='Klaviyo'?'Gift purchase and redemption':a[0]==='Omnisend'?'Holiday gift-card campaign':a[0]==='Sequenzy'?'Delivery and redemption sequence':a[0]==='Brevo'?'Transactional gift delivery':'Gift-card announcement'}</td><td>{a[3]}</td></tr>)}</tbody></table>{apps.map(a=><section><h2>{a[0]} for gift cards</h2><p><strong>Best for:</strong> {a[1]}. {a[0]} is useful when purchaser, recipient, delivery, balance, and redemption states remain distinct. Do not infer recipient consent or purchase intent from the purchaser’s email address without a clear permission basis.</p><p><strong>Why it stands out:</strong> {a[2]}. Start with one delivery and redemption path, then review redemption, support questions, unsubscribes, and repeat orders. Gift-card performance varies by season and offer; avoid universal revenue claims.</p><table><tbody><tr><th>Pros</th><td>{a[2]}; supports a state-aware gifting test; can use Shopify events.</td></tr><tr><th>Cons</th><td>{a[3]}; gift-card integrations and channel volume affect cost.</td></tr><tr><th>Pricing context</th><td>Verify official plans plus gift-card, contacts, sends, and SMS costs.</td></tr><tr><th>Source</th><td><a href={a[4]} rel="nofollow">Official product information</a></td></tr></tbody></table></section>)}<h2>Decision guide</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Gift-card priority</th><th>Start with</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Purchaser and redemption states</td><td>Klaviyo</td><td>Flexible events and profiles.</td></tr><tr><td>Focused delivery sequence</td><td>Sequenzy</td><td>Simple operations.</td></tr><tr><td>Native announcement</td><td>Shopify Email</td><td>Fast setup.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>See the <a href="/shopify-email">Shopify email overview</a>, <a href="/alternatives">alternatives library</a>, and <a href="/use-cases/holiday-gifting">holiday-gifting guide</a>.</p></main></BaseLayout>
